location.fullValue: The Pioneer (C470) Plan, Pine Lake Cove - Classic Series

data.description: Gorgeous,one story home w/4 bedrooms,3 full baths w/brick & stone exterior.Nestled in the heart of Montgomery & zoned to Montgomery ISD!Boasting an inviting open floor plan & TONS OF UPGRADES THROUGHOUT!The main living area features vinyl plank flooring that seamlessly guides you through the home. Custom shade blinds in living room & primary bedroom areas. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary dream,complete w/a generously sized island & pantry,sleek granite countertops & an exquisite subway tile backsplash.Retreat to the expansive primary bedroom,enhanced by vinyl plank flooring,offering a tranquil haven.The ensuite bathroom exudes elegance & convenience featuring Lg walk-in closet, dual sinks,separate shower & garden tub!Step outside to the covered back patio,thoughtfully designed w/retractable sunscreens,providing the perfect setting for relaxation. Additionally, this home is equipped w/a GENERATOR for added peace of mind.Sprinkler system,tankless hot water heater & so much more!
